race_comments: Grant Enfinger won the NextEra Energy 250 at Daytona International Speedway, his third victory in the NASCAR Gander RV & Outdoors Truck Series. Prior to the start of the race, the following truck(s) dropped to the rear of the field under penalty for the reasons indicated: Nos. 44, 33 (unapproved adjustments).
